data.title: Tyrese Haliburton has recently taken the crown of 'ugly but weirdly effective jump shot' from retired NBA champion Shawn Marion. Haliburton...
data.meta_description:
13 likes, 2 comments - techfoultimes on November 1, 2023: "Tyrese Haliburton has recently taken the crown of 'ugly but weirdly effective jump shot' from retired NBA champion Shawn Marion. Haliburton responded the crowning stating "I don't know why I shoot like this but I do, and honestly I just chuck it up and it seems to go in". 

Marion was asked for comment but was unable to speak with reporters due to being too upset over the news. Pundits had Marion holding the crown for far longer than he did, making Marions reaction to the news understandable. 

#nba #nbamemes #jokes #funny #marion #haliburton #pacers #mavs #jumpshot #uglyjumper #jumper".
